<% content_for :title do %>MIT Model United Nations Conference - Info & Fees<% end %>

  <div style = "color:rgba(26,26,26,.7);" class="garamond main main-text">
    <p class="te">
      In order to ensure participation in MITMUNC XI 2019, faculty advisors and delegates must pay special attention to our conference deadlines as well as apply early and properly.<BR/><BR/>
      MITMUNC is <b>*only*</b> open to high school students in all nations across the world and not to those currently enrolled in a full-time college or university. <BR/>
      The following was the schedule followed for MITMUNC X 2018.
    </p>

    <div id="conference-info">
    <div style="color: #BD2031" class="text-center">
      <h2>Important Dates <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-calendar"></span></h2>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-6">
      <h3 class="date-heading">Mid-September 2017</h3>
      <p class="bulleted-info">Regular Registration opens</p>
      <h3 class="date-heading">November 24th, 2017</h3>
      <p class="bulleted-info">Regular Registration closes</p>
      <p class="bulleted-info">*All conference fees due.* Failure to provide payment will result in relegation to waitlist.</p>
      <p class="bulleted-info">Financial Assistance application due</p>
      <h3 class="date-heading">December 2nd, 2017</h3>
      <p class="bulleted-info">Waitlist application opens. All conference fees due immediately upon acceptance from waitlist.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-6">
      <h3 class="date-heading">January 5th, 2018</h3>
      <p class="bulleted-info">Waitlist application closes.</p>
      <p class="bulleted-info">Last day for to request refund on conference fees. No refund request shall be accepted afterwards.</p>
        <h3 class="date-heading">January 12th, 2018</h3>
        <p class="bulleted-info">Position Papers due from delegates. Late penalty applied afterwards.</p>
        <h3 class="date-heading">February 9-11th, 2018</h3>
        <p class="bulleted-info spacer">MITMUNC X 2018</p>
        <BR/>
        <BR/>
        <BR/>
        <!-- These ^three breaks are necessary to make following conference fees header not go to right when window is maximized -->
    </div>


    <div style="color: #BD2031" class="text-center">
      <h2>Conference Fees <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-usd"></span></h2>
    </div>
      <div class="text-center"><h3 class="date-heading">Schools with more than 5 delegates</h3><BR/>
          <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-chevron-right"></span>75 USD school fee<BR/>
          <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-chevron-right"></span>70 USD per individual delegate<BR/>
      </div>
      </BR>
      </BR>

      <div class="text-center">
        <h3 class="date-heading">Schools with less than 5 delegates</h3><BR/>
        Exempt from school fee<BR/>
        <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-chevron-right"></span>70 USD per individual delegate<BR/><BR/>
      </div>
      <div class="text-center">
        After completing the initial registration process, schools will be asked to complete their payment online, which is the preferred method of payment. Schools may also send a check or submit a domestic or international wire transfer. <BR/>
        To process payments, a school should collect all fees from delegates and pay once.
        Once payment has been received, the designated school advisor will receive a final notice of registration confirmation.<BR/>
        Payment <i>must</i> be received upon specified conference deadlines to secure your delegation's spots in MITMUNC. Failure to complete this process will result in a delegation's spots being released to waitlist due to high demand.
        <BR/><BR/>
        <h3 class="date-heading">Financial Aid</h3>If payment of conference fees is a barrier to participation to MITMUNC, you may apply for financial aid to assist in reduction of conference fees.
      </p>
      <BR/>
      <div class="text-center" style="color:#BD2031">
        <h2>Conference Schedule <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-calendar"></span></h2>
      </div>

      <p> The following is the schedule for MITMUNC X 2018, Feb 9th-11th.</p>
      <div class="col-md-6">
        <h3 class="date-heading">Friday, February 9th</h3>
        <p class="bulleted-info">3-5PM: Delegation Check-In, <i>Marriot Ballroom Lobby</i></p>
        <p class="bulleted-info">5-6PM: Opening Ceremonies, <i>Marriot Ballroom</i></p>
        <p class="bulleted-info">6:30PM- 9PM: Committee Session I <i>E51 (Tang Center) Classrooms </i></p>
        <h3 class="date-heading">Saturday, February 10th</h3>
        <p class="bulleted-info">9:30AM-12:30PM: Committee Session II</p>
        <p class="bulleted-info">12:30PM-2PM: Lunch Break</p>
        <p class="bulleted-info">2PM-5PM: Committee Session III</p>
        <p class="bulleted-info">5PM-6:30PM: Dinner Break</p>
        <p class="bulleted-info">6:30PM-8:30 PM: Committee Session IV</p>
        <p class="bulleted-info">7PM: Advisor Meeting <i>E51 (Tang Center) Room 361</i></p>
        <p class="bulleted-info">9:30PM-12 AM: Delegate Dance <i> Lobdell, Building W20 (Student Center)</i></p>
      </div>
      <div class="col-md-6">
        <h3 class="date-heading">Sunday, February 11th</h3>
        <p class="bulleted-info">9:30AM-11:30 PM: Committee Session V</p>
        <p class="bulleted-info">11:30PM-1 PM: Lunch Break</p>
        <p class="bulleted-info">1 PM: Closing Ceremonies <i> Kresge Auditorium </i></p>
      </div>
      <BR/>
      <BR/>
