      <!-- Accomodations -->
      <div class="col-md-12 text-center main-text ">
        <div class="text-center" style="color:#BD2031">
          <h2 class="garamond">Accommodations <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-home"></span></h2>
        </div>
        <p class="description">MITMUNC X 2018 will be held at the Massachusetts Institute of Technology campus. Following our usual annual agreement, MITMUNC has arranged a discounted
          rooming rate for delegates and advisors to stay at the Boston Marriot Cambridge,
          located at Kendall Square on 50 Broadway, Cambridge, MA 02142, United States.</p>
          <p class="description">Discounted room rate*: $149.00, plus tax, per night</p>
          <p class="description">The Kendall Square Marriott is the closest hotel to conference venues,
            a mere 7 minutes walking distance.<BR/><BR/>
            <strong><a href="http://www.marriott.com/hotels/travel/boscb-boston-marriott-cambridge/">Boston Marriot Cambridge</a></strong><BR/>
            50 Broadway, Cambridge, MA 02142<BR/>
            Hotel: (617) 494-6600<BR/>



            </p>
      </div>
      <div class="text-center garamond spacer">

        <img src="http://cache.marriott.com/propertyimages/b/boscb/boscb_main02_r.jpg?resize=0.5x:0.5x" style="width: 70%" />
